who's the grandson of Sam

00:09:31.890 --> 00:09:33.750
Walton, the founder of Walmart.

00:09:33.750 --> 00:09:37.200
So he can pretty much
do anything he wants,

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:38.400
and what does he like to do?

