a little bit about me.

00:12:31.550 --> 00:12:34.820
In the top left
corner, you'll see me.

00:12:34.820 --> 00:12:39.440
I'm actually sitting in a
Cessna 172, here at Hanscom,

00:12:39.440 --> 00:12:41.390
and I'm doing my engine run-up.

00:12:41.390 --> 00:12:44.330
And what do you
see out the window?

00:12:44.330 --> 00:12:47.710
Does anyone recognize it?

