00:33:04.290 --> 00:33:07.110
power on a big jet?

00:33:07.110 --> 00:33:08.610
Big jets, the
flight controls are

00:33:08.610 --> 00:33:11.550
too heavy to be
operated by a human,

00:33:11.550 --> 00:33:12.920
so you need hydraulic power.

00:33:12.920 --> 00:33:15.973
Basically, there may still
be steel cables going out

00:33:15.973 --> 00:33:17.640
to the flight controls,
but they're just

00:33:17.640 --> 00:33:19.770
modulating hydraulic pressure.

00:33:19.770 --> 00:33:21.780
How do you generate
hydraulic pressure?

00:33:21.780 --> 00:33:26.250
There's a big motor to
pump the hydraulics,

00:33:26.250 --> 00:33:30.360
and it's easier to run a
big motor with AC power

00:33:30.360 --> 00:33:35.130
compared to DC power, and the
engines are also spinning.

00:33:35.130 --> 00:33:37.500
So if you just think
about Maxwell's equations,

00:33:37.500 --> 00:33:41.820
it's simpler to run AC for
that, and also, of course, you

00:33:41.820 --> 00:33:44.410
can have higher voltage
and transform it down.

00:33:44.410 --> 00:33:48.340
And then for the electronics,
DC power is what they want.

00:33:48.340 --> 00:33:52.850
So that's why the DC's in there,
to run radios and so forth.